        <abstract> 
<p>Sends thanks for recent specimen, which gave him conclusive evidence that <hi rend="italic">Verruca</hi> acts only on calcareous rocks.</p> 
            <p>Asks for a reference on carbonic acid.</p>
            <p>Is glad CSB progresses in research on spider-like Crustacea.</p>
        </abstract>
